data.text:
Valdosta, GA, USA

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 30.832703, -83.278488.

Valdosta is a city in southern Georgia, a very important commercial and transportation center, both for Georgia and Florida. It is an industrial hub, with a few plants producing pine lumber, pulpwood, tobacco, and so on. It is also a center of shopping, with large shopping areas and the best shopping malls in the state. There are a few great colleges and a university in the city.
